#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.57"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.57:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Ānāpānavagga → ānāpānādipeyyālo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.57:0.2"
msgid "7. Ānāpānavagga "
msgstr "7. Breathing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 57. Aṭṭhikamahapphalasutta → aṭṭhikasuttaṃ (bj) | aṭṭhika mahapphala-mahānisaṃsā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Aṭṭhikamahapphalasutta "
msgstr "57. A Skeleton "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.129, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.57:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.57:1.2"
msgid "“Aṭṭhikasaññā, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when the perception of a skeleton is developed and cultivated it’s very fruitful and beneficial. "

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.3"
msgid "Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññā kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā? "
msgstr "How so? "

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the perception of a skeleton together with the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.5"
msgid "Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññā evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how the perception of a skeleton, when developed and cultivated, is very fruitful and beneficial.” "

#. HTML: <h2>
msgctxt "sn46.57:1.6"
msgid "Aññataraphalasutta "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: p_14S5_666, sc2
msgctxt "sn46.57:2.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhikasaññāya, bhikkhave, bhāvitāya bahulīkatāya dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā. "
msgstr "“When the perception of a skeleton is developed and cultivated you can expect one of two results: enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-return. "

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.2"
msgid "Kathaṃ bhāvitāya ca kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññāya kathaṃ bahulīkatāya dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā? "
msgstr "How so?...” "

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pe … aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ bhāvitāya kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññāya evaṃ bahulīkatāya dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "sn46.57:2.5"
msgid "Mahatthasutta "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: p_14S5_667, sc3
msgctxt "sn46.57:3.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhikasaññā, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahato atthāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when the perception of a skeleton is developed and cultivated it leads to great benefit. "

